    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I decided to start blogging again and picked
<a href="http://octopress.org/">Octopress</a>. While setting up I found some hickups I
want to document.</p>

<ul>
<li>You have to build the latest ruby from source via rvm. For strange reasons ruby 1.9.3 didn&#8217;t work for me.</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rvm install ruby-1.9.3-p194</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li>Don&#8217;t prefix your Twitter name with an &#8220;@&#8221; in _config.yml. It results in an ugly stacktrace stating nonsense.</li>
</ul>


<p>That&#8217;s it. The rest is pretty straight forward.</p>
